    "detailed_description": "<h1>Be part of our Community</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/aefa54e722fe1472318ab21256584926.avif?t=1764059680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras_big/aefa54e722fe1472318ab21256584926.avif?t=1764059680 width=800 height=214 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Acerca del juego</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/182a95e520f18cf150120c39775a4155.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/0dc513f4fdfd8131f158ba3be49dcc5b.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¡Invita a un amigo a unirse gratis y trabajad juntos para descubrir misterios, explorar entornos espeluznantes y huir de criaturas malignas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El juego es una mezcla de interacciones tiernas y espeluznantes, lleno de misterios cautivadores. Forma equipo con tu compañero de coop y embarcaos en una aventura que es tanto inquietante como emotiva, llena de momentos emocionales. ¡Sumérgete en este viaje espeluznante pero acogedor junto a tu amigo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/821d62aa28491fea9a84a031c76ba964.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jugarás como cachorros y podrás cavar, olfatear, ladrar y otras divertidas cosas de cachorros!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elige tu raza de perro favorita e involúcrate en el mundo de los cachorros. ¡Disfruta de la vida juguetona de un cachorro con amigos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/d816eb9df4401e18a32fe2cab16ff223.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El mejor amigo humano de nuestros pequeños cachorros ha sido secuestrado por criaturas malignas y encerrado en una mansión encantada. ¡Para liberarlo tendrás que enfrentarte a diversos horrores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >En Haunted Paws, cada criatura siniestra oculta un oscuro pasado. Derrotalas para descubrir sus secretos y liberarlas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/832a699dfaee55fcef4d0cab99609750.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crea un personaje de juego que se parezca a tu perro real! Elige de una amplia selección de razas, personaliza el color del pelaje y añade detalles únicos que capturan la esencia de tu mascota. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luego, viste a tu perro con varios accesorios divertidos para mejorar su aspecto. Una vez que tu personaje esté listo, lánzate a una aventura emocionante como tu propio cachorro.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3f16421e8ad944cab34eb7a6531d2e65.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/182a95e520f18cf150120c39775a4155.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/a48384dea357951a4867111901d7df0a.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/0dc513f4fdfd8131f158ba3be49dcc5b.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¡Invita a un amigo a unirse gratis y trabajad juntos para descubrir misterios, explorar entornos espeluznantes y huir de criaturas malignas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El juego es una mezcla de interacciones tiernas y espeluznantes, lleno de misterios cautivadores. Forma equipo con tu compañero de coop y embarcaos en una aventura que es tanto inquietante como emotiva, llena de momentos emocionales. ¡Sumérgete en este viaje espeluznante pero acogedor junto a tu amigo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/dec3e5684d55a5fbeb720babfe0f675e.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/821d62aa28491fea9a84a031c76ba964.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jugarás como cachorros y podrás cavar, olfatear, ladrar y otras divertidas cosas de cachorros!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elige tu raza de perro favorita e involúcrate en el mundo de los cachorros. ¡Disfruta de la vida juguetona de un cachorro con amigos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3c6eee990cd50cb4d8b5419d1d581fda.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/d816eb9df4401e18a32fe2cab16ff223.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El mejor amigo humano de nuestros pequeños cachorros ha sido secuestrado por criaturas malignas y encerrado en una mansión encantada. ¡Para liberarlo tendrás que enfrentarte a diversos horrores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >En Haunted Paws, cada criatura siniestra oculta un oscuro pasado. Derrotalas para descubrir sus secretos y liberarlas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.poster.avif?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.webm?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/9316ce18bb4b871208ded5f1459d3628.mp4?t=1764059680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/832a699dfaee55fcef4d0cab99609750.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crea un personaje de juego que se parezca a tu perro real! Elige de una amplia selección de razas, personaliza el color del pelaje y añade detalles únicos que capturan la esencia de tu mascota. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luego, viste a tu perro con varios accesorios divertidos para mejorar su aspecto. Una vez que tu personaje esté listo, lánzate a una aventura emocionante como tu propio cachorro.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861080/extras/3f16421e8ad944cab34eb7a6531d2e65.webp?t=1764059680\" width=620 height=35 /></span></p>",
    "short_description": "Haunted Paws es un juego de terror cooperativo y acogedor donde jugarás como dos cachorros intentando rescatar a su amigo humano en una mansión embrujada. ¡Crea tu cachorro, explora entornos espeluznantes y derrota a criaturas malignas en una aventura llena de acción!",
